CodeSystemDisplayDefinition
submittedhttp://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/adjudicationSubmitted AmountThe total submitted amount for the claim or group or line item.

eligiblehttp://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/adjudicationEligible AmountAmount of the change which is considered for adjudication.
deductiblehttp://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/adjudicationDeductibleAmount deducted from the eligible amount prior to adjudication.
benefithttp://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/adjudicationBenefit AmountAmount payable under the coverage
coinsurancehttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSCoinsuranceThe amount the insured individual pays, as a set percentage of the cost of covered medical services, as an out-of-pocket payment to the provider. Example: Insured pays 20% and the insurer pays 80%.

priorpayerpaidhttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSPrior payer paidThe reduction in the payment amount to reflect the carrier as a secondary payor.
paidbypatienthttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSPaid by patientThe amount paid by the patient at the point of service.
paidtopatienthttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSPaid to patientpaid to patient
paidtoproviderhttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSPaid to providerThe amount paid to the provider.
memberliabilityhttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSMember liabilityThe amount of the member's liability.
discounthttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSDiscountThe amount of the discount
drugcosthttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSDrug costPrice paid for the drug excluding mfr or other discounts. It typically is the sum of the following components: ingredient cost, dispensing fee, sales tax, and vaccine administration

  • Benefit Payment Status v0.4.1 (ValueSet)

CodeSystemDisplayDefinition
submittedhttp://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/adjudicationSubmitted AmountThe total submitted amount for the claim or group or line item.
copayhttp://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/adjudicationCoPayPatient Co-Payment
eligiblehttp://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/adjudicationEligible AmountAmount of the change which is considered for adjudication.
deductiblehttp://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/adjudicationDeductibleAmount deducted from the eligible amount prior to adjudication.
benefithttp://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/adjudicationBenefit AmountAmount payable under the coverage
coinsurancehttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSCoinsuranceThe amount the insured individual pays, as a set percentage of the cost of covered medical services, as an out-of-pocket payment to the provider. Example: Insured pays 20% and the insurer pays 80%.
noncoveredhttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSNoncoveredThe portion of the cost of this service that was deemed not eligible by the insurer because the service or member was not covered by the subscriber contract.
priorpayerpaidhttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSPrior payer paidThe reduction in the payment amount to reflect the carrier as a secondary payor.
paidbypatienthttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSPaid by patientThe amount paid by the patient at the point of service.
paidtopatienthttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSPaid to patientpaid to patient
paidtoproviderhttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSPaid to providerThe amount paid to the provider.
memberliabilityhttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSMember liabilityThe amount of the member's liability.
discounthttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSDiscountThe amount of the discount
drugcosthttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSDrug costPrice paid for the drug excluding mfr or other discounts. It typically is the sum of the following components: ingredient cost, dispensing fee, sales tax, and vaccine administration
innetworkhttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSin-networkin-network
outofnetworkhttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSout-of-networkout-of-network
otherhttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/PayerAdjudicationCategoryCSotherother
denialreasonhttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/ClaimAdjudicationCategoryCSpayment denial reasonUndefined
allowedunitshttp://hl7.org/fhir/us/carin-bb/CodeSystem/ClaimAdjudicationCategoryCSallowed unitsUndefined
